burlap.behavior.singleagent.interfaces.rlglue.common

Class RLGLueQlearningFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • burlap.behavior.singleagent.interfaces.rlglue.common.RLGLueQlearningFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RLGlueLearningAgentFactory
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RLGlueSARSALambdaFactory

    public class RLGLueQlearningFactory
extends java.lang.Object
implements RLGlueLearningAgentFactory
    This class is used to setup a BURLAP Q-learning algorithm with RLGlue. It can be launched from a main method and have various Q-Learning parameters specified by command line options. Use the "--help" option to see full list.
    Author:
    James MacGlashan
